{"Sid":0,"Did":126716,"Id":"602974","Title":"大洲天主堂","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-11/f52184de-33a1-4d5a-8a72-52adcf89a439/collection/477beb92-f09d-44ba-85e8-3fe400977e5f/109-sea-pa-2343-202011081007155fa750e96a0460.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n　　大洲天主堂為羅東聖母靈醫會之義大利神父於戰後所建，初期建立天主堂時，租借當地居民的店面作為宣傳福音的居所，當時四周多為水田，房屋甚少，經過神父的努力，教友漸漸聚集。1960年代，大洲天主堂正式落成於上將路上，並由孔德祿神父擔任該堂神父，並於1965年在教堂旁開設幼稚園，為當地帶來教育機會。\n\n　　在台美尚未斷交時，天主堂成為三星鄉重要的美援發放處，領受麵粉、沙拉油，為許多當地耆老之共同記憶。現今，年輕人因長年工作在外，目前教友普遍年紀較大，教堂使用頻率也漸漸降低，僅零星使用。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.729731","Keyword_Latitude":"24.693452","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/69A87C1D-9B47-4DA4-9D80-FCBE83F661B3","Original_Identifier":"602974","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"孔德祿 / 美援 / 靈醫會","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2021/01/05 15:34:24","timelines":"","place":"","address":"宜蘭縣三星鄉上將路二段383號","longitude":"121.729731","latitude":"24.693452","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"羅東聖母醫院-羅東聖母靈醫會","writer":"莊文生;林冠旻","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-11/f52184de-33a1-4d5a-8a72-52adcf89a439/collectionOpen/11b57f29-ab72-447d-8659-6cf292f86708/109-sea-pa-2343-re-202011061253525fa4cacc781550.jpg"}}